---
title: Spicy Cajun Chicken Breast Stovetop Risotto with Lemon Crumb and Peas
description: Making a risotto on the hob or stove is simpler than you think, with only three stirs needed to absorb the stock and flavours. This Spicy Cajun Chicken Breast Stovetop Risotto uses Cajun spice mix for a punchy flavour.
